headline: Duke Energy Foundation commits $500,000 to support local environmental impact programs across North Carolina

headline: Duke Energy and GE Vernova announce significant arrangement for gas turbines and associated equipment
summary: Duke Energy (NYSE: DUK) and GE Vernova (NYSE: GEV) announce a significant partnership for natural gas turbines and other associated equipment to meet the growing needs of advanced manufacturing, data centers and population growth.
